name: Jelly Match 3 Deluxe
description:
Jelly Match 3 Deluxe is the highly addictive casual game with unlimited interesting puzzle game levels. Jelly Match 3 Deluxe is consists of unlimited puzzle gaming levels & better than any match three game. Each level is like new puzzle to solve. You have to complete each level in limited moves. If you like challenges than this game is just for you. Jelly Match 3 Deluxe is complete package of fun and addiction for Match three kind game lovers.

FEATURES:
- Nice game music
- Stuck in any level??? Just use the power-up to clear the level
- Awesome game graphics
- All POWER-UPS are freely available in Jelly Match 3 Deluxe

Share this game with friends & compete them with your highscore...
